data.description: Welcome to tranquil living in Filer, Idaho! This charming property offers the perfect blend of quiet country living and convenient access to town, just 10 minutes away. Situated on a spacious acre of well-kept land, this home provides a serene escape from the hustle and bustle. Acreage features a detached garage, providing ample space for parking, RV space, and storage. Whether you're a nature enthusiast or simply seeking a peaceful retreat, this residence caters to a lifestyle of comfort and convenience. Embrace the opportunity to bring your rural dreams to life – this property allows for up to two horses, cows, or sheep, making it an ideal space for those with a passion for agriculture or simply desiring a bit more space to roam. Experience the freedom of open spaces, the convenience of nearby amenities, and the potential for a variety of outdoor activities right in your backyard. Don't miss the chance to make this haven your home!
